<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="job-n">job <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dʒɒb/    美 /dʒɑːb/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>工作；职业：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>apply for / quit a job</strong>
求职/辞职</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>be out of a job</strong> 
失业</p></div>

<h4 id="2-task">2.★ <strong>(单件) 工作；活儿 (task)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You do a good / bad job. 
你干得好/不好。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>职责；任务：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It's not my job.
这不是我的职责。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>jobless  /'dʒɒbləs/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Since I was a kid, I've considered different job I would like to do.  （2019全国 改错）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. job→jobs  </p></div>